Package org.apache.hadoop.hbase.mapreduce

Class ImportTsv

java.lang.Object
org.apache.hadoop.conf.Configured
org.apache.hadoop.hbase.mapreduce.ImportTsv
All Implemented Interfaces:
org.apache.hadoop.conf.Configurable, org.apache.hadoop.util.Tool
@Public public class ImportTsv extends org.apache.hadoop.conf.Configured implements org.apache.hadoop.util.Tool
Tool to import data from a TSV file. This tool is rather simplistic - it doesn't do any quoting or escaping, but is useful for many data loads.
